                                        ],
                                        "body": "The provisions of Chapters 12 through 24 shall regulate the design, installation, maintenance, <span class=\"u-italic\">alteration</span> and inspection of mechanical systems that are permanently installed and used to control environmental conditions within buildings. These chapters shall also regulate those mechanical systems, system components, <span class=\"u-italic\">equipment</span> and <span class=\"u-italic\">appliances</span> specifically addressed in this code.",
